snippet.title: Re-Exit Trailer (Spot the anomaly horror game)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Re-Exit, a psychological horror, spot the anomaly game that challenges your perception and attention to detail. Trapped in a temporal loop caused by an unexplained anomaly, your mission is to observe your surroundings carefully and report any irregularities to find a way out.

Steam Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3318470/ReExit/
